</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/other-training-for-agency-and-bank-workers--dr-richard-dune--1682008740086.png?v=1682008743" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/other-training-for-agency-and-bank-workers--dr-richard-dune--1682008740086.png?v=1682008743 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/t/33/assets/other-training-for-agency-and-bank-workers--dr-richard-dune--1682008740086_500x.png?v=1682008743 320w" width="1382" height="922" alt="Other training for agency and bank workers - Richard Dune, PhD -" title="Other training for agency and bank workers - Richard Dune, PhD -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-bXTejn eKvewz pf-277_"/><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-278_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-280_">Locum/agency and bank staff generally receive free statutory and mandatory training, but any further career development training is self-funded. NHS Professionals (temporary NHS staff), agencies, and locum workers can access most of their training courses online.
